  ('dietitian-moex-03209', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '行政院衛生署公告之現行「國人膳食營養素參考攝取量」中建議13～18歲青少年每日鈣質之足夠攝取量 （adequate intake）為：', '["800毫克", "1000毫克", "1200毫克", "2000毫克"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-03210', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-102-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '訂定「國人膳食營養素參考攝取量」時，以能滿足健康人群中每一個人為原則，由實驗或觀察數據估算 出的攝取量，稱為：', '["平均需要量（EAR）", "足夠攝取量（AI）", "建議攝取量（RDA）", "上限攝取量（UL）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:31:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aab8dcf25588", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fbd287ac8cfb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "106", "s": "0305", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
